  I. Chin-sit8 e5 Toa3
  “Sou2-i2 tioh8 khia7-chai7, eng7 chin-sit8 e5 toa3 ha5 io.” Che si7 Siong7-te3 e5 chin-sit8, m7 si7 li2 ka-ki7--e5. Tioh8 ha5 chit-e5 chhin-chhiuN7 chin kiong5 e5 tian7-khi3 toa3, “Siong7-te3 si7 chin-sit8, sou2-i2 I sou2 kong2 tak8 ku3-oe7 lan2 thang sin3.” Chit tiau5 toa3 hou7 Seng3-chheh chiaN5 choe3 chin u7 ke3-tat8; Siong7-te3 e5 oe7 na7 jip8 li2 e5 sim-lai7 na2 chhim, chiu7 oe7 hou7 li2 tit-tioh8 khui3-lat8 kap khoai3-lok8, chiu7-si7 pat8-lang5 sou2 boe7 chhek-tok8--e5. Tioh8 ha5 chit tiau5 toa3, che si7 Siong7-te3 e5 chian3-kah e5 thau5 chit8 hang7. Na7 bo5 chit hang7, ki5-u5-e5 li2 chiu7 long2 boe7 tit-tioh8. 
  Goa2 ai3 ka7 lin2 kong2, goa2 thau5 chit8 pai2 chaiN2-iuN7 ha5 chit tiau5 toa3, ia7 hou7 goa2 tek-seng3. Goa2 iau2-be7 chap8-saN he3 e5 si5, goa2 chin ti3-i3, chi3-goan7 ai3 choe3 Ki-tok e5 peng; na7 an2-ni goa2 sui-bong2 hou7 lui5 ham2 si2, a2-si7 pat8-khoan2 gui5-hiam2 e5 su7, kau3 ti7 goa2 e5 sin-chiuN7, goa2 tek-khak ku2-tng5 un2-tang3 bo5 kiaN. Goa2 chiu7 ki5-to2 chiu7-kun7 Chu2 Ia5-sou; ka7 I kong2 goa2 ai3 choe3 I e5 kiaN2-ji5, chong2-si7 toa7 e5 tui3-tek8 teh khoaN3 goa2, i put-si5 ti7 goa2 e5 hi7-khang-piN soe3-a2-siaN kong2, “Ia5-sou Ki-tok m7 chiap-lap8 li2, in-ui7 li2 iau2-be7 chap8-hun e5 jiat8-sim, lai5 chin7 li2 sou2 eng-kai tioh8 chin7-e5.” Goa2 chai che si7 chin-sit8, sou2-i2 put-chi2 kiaN-hiaN5. Chong2-si7 goa2 bat Ia5-sou pun2-sin sou2 kong2 e5 oe7, chiu7-si7 ti7 Iok-han7 Hok-im-toan7, kong2, “Hoan7-na7 chiu7-kun7 Goa2-e5, Goa2 tek-khak bo5 pang3-sak i.” Sou2-i2 goa2 chiu7 chai, Ia5-sou u7 nng7-hang7 hoat-tou7 thang choe3 na7-tiaN7. I na7 m7 si7 pang3-sak goa2, chiu7-si7 chiap-lap8 goa2. I kong2 tek-khak bo5 pang3-sak goa2, an2-ni I tek-khak chiap-lap8 goa2. “Siong7-te3 e5 oe7 si7 chin-sit8, sou2-i2 goa2 thang sin3, m7-bian2 u7 giau5-gi5.” Che si7 Siong7-te3 chin-sit8 e5 toa3, sou2-i2 goa2 tit-tioh8, ia7 ka7 i ha5 teh. Goa2 pun2-sin siuN7, “Siong7 te3 e5 oe7 si7 chin-sit8, goa2 thang sin3 i; an2-ni I bo5 pang3-sak goa2, I u7 chiap-lap8 goa2, goa2 si7 I e5, ia7 I si7 goa2 e5.” Goa2 na2 oe7 chai chit-e5 ? Tok8 tok8 in-ui7 I e5 oe7 u7 an2-ni kong2, koh “I e5 oe7 si7 chin-sit8, sou2-i2 goa2 thang sin3 i.” 
  Tui3 an2-ni toa7 e5 tui3-tek8, put-tek-i2 tioh8 thian2-khui toa7 e5 sit8, chiam7-si5 li7-khui khi3, chhin-chhiuN7 A-pho-lun5 ti7 Ku-khiam e5 soaN-kok sou2 choe3 chit8-iuN7. Hit si5 si7 tang-thiN e5 cha2-khi2 si5, goa2 u7 ha5 Siong7-te3 chin-sit8 e5 toa3, sou2-i2 chiah tit-tioh8 toa7 tek-seng3. “I e5 oe7 si7 chin-sit8, sou2-i2 goa2 thang sin3 i.” 
