  Hit poaN3 tiam2 cheng ku2 e5 ki5-to2 si7 te7-it oh e5 kang-tiaN5. Goa2 sit8-chai7 chhin-chhiuN7 boe7 siu2 goa2 sou2 iok-sok e5 hun7-giah8. Chit8 am3 goa2 u7 kong2-beng5 goa2 e5 sit-bang7, kong2, “Goa2 e5 ki5-to2 long2 boe7 choe3 sim2-mih8 kong-hau7; in-ui7 hiah-e5 ki5-to2 chin bo5 oah8-khi3 koh leng2-tam7, sou2-i2 Siong7-te3 bo5 beh thiaN. Chong2-si7 goa2 chai Ha5-li2 e5 ki5-to2 put-chi2 u7 hau7-lek8.” 
  In-ui7 an2-ni, sui5-si5 chhut chit hang7 bun7-toe5: “ChaiN2-iuN7 Ha5-li2 e5 ki5-to2 oe7 tit-tioh8 un2-chun2?” In3-tap sui5-si5 chhut-lai5 : “In-ui7 Ha5-li2 eng7 Ki-tok e5 mia5 kap I e5 gi7 lai5 chhin-kun7 Siong7-te3, m7 si7 eng7 i ka-ki7 e5.” 
  Au7-lai5 te7 ji7 e5 bun7-toe5: “Goa2 eng7 sim2-mih8 lang5 e5 mia5 kap gi7 lai5 chhin-kun7 Siong7-te3 ?” In3-tap sui5-si5 koh chhut-lai5 : “Goa2 e5 chu2-chi2 tu2-tu2 kap Ha5-li2 saN-tang5. Goa2 eng7 Ki-tok e5 mia5 kap I e5 gi7 lai5 chhin-kun7 I.” Au7-lai5 goa2 chin hoaN-hi2 koh ho2-taN2, in-ui7 goa2 pun2-sin kap goa2 e5 ki5-to2 e5 khoat-ham7, i2-keng long2 siau-biat8 bo5 khoaN3-kiN3 lah, sou2-i2 goa2 chin eng5-kng tiam3 ti7 bo5 ha5-hun5 gi7 e5 thiaN3-thang3 e5 tiong-kan. Goa2 u7 tit-tioh8 Gi7 e5 Hou7-sim-kiaN3. 
  Goa2 ai3 kong2 chit8 e5 phi3-ju7 hou7 lin2 khah beng5. Iok-han7 si7 Ki-tok e5 peng, i kui7 ti7 Siong7-te3 e5 bin7-cheng5; chong2-si7 i iu5-goan5 chin sit-taN2, in-ui7 i chai choe7 tang7. I kui7-teh e5 si5, mou5-kui2 chhin-chhiuN7 ti7 sin-piN, ai3 pe2-pak8 i, hou7 i koh-khah sit-taN2. Mou5-kui2 ti7 i e5 hi-khang-piN kong2, “Li2 lai5 ki5-kiu5 Siong7-te3 chin ho2, in-ui7 li2 si7 cha3-khi e5 lang5.” 
  Iok-han7 kong2, “Kiam2-chhai2 u7 iaN2.” 
  “Li2 tu2-tu2 si7 chhin-chhiuN7 Thou2-ni2-ki5 e5 hong5-te3 hiah kou3-ki2 e5 lang5.” 
  Iok-han7 kong2, “Phah-sng3 kaN2 u7 iaN2.” “Li2 si7 thai5-si2 lang5-e5, in-ui7 li2 kin-a2-jit8 bo5 in-toaN lam7-sam2 siu7-khi3 lang5”. 
  Li2 chit pai2 an2-ni chiu7 tioh8, i an2-ni in3, ia7 tak8-pou7 na2 poah8-loh8 na2 chhim. Chong2-si7 thiN u7 chi2-si7 i e5 sou2 siuN7. I chhun-chhiu2 jip8 heng-cheng5 e5 te7-a2, theh8 chit8 pun2 phou7-a2 chhut-lai5. I chiu7 kong2,“TaN koh kong2, goa2 iau2 u7 choe3 sim2-mih8 m7-tioh8 e5 su7.” 
  Hit pun2 si7 “ko3-sou3 chia2” sou2 hou7 i e5 bok8-liok8, lai7-tiog put-chi2 tng5 koh si7 sit8-chai7-e5. Choe7-koe3 u7-e5 i i2-keng long2 chai liau2, chong2-si7 u7-e5 iau2-be7 bat siuN7-tioh8. Long2 khoaN3 chheng-chho2 liau2, i chiu7 thiah chit8 tiuN theh8 hou7 mou5-kui2, kong2, “Eng7 chit tiuN theh8 khi3 hou7 Ia5-sou. I long2 taN goa2 e5 choe7 lah, goa2 tit-tioh8 I e5 gi7. Li2 iau2 oe7 koh chhe7-chhut sim2-mih8 ha5-hun5 mah ?” 
  Toa7 e5 tui3-tek8 sui5-si5 li7-khui Iok-han7, ia7 bo5 beh theh8 hit tiuN bok8-liok8. Chit e5 siau3-lian5 e5 peng kau-chian3 u7 tek-seng3, in-ui7 i u7 tit-tioh8 Ki-tok Gi7 e5 Hou7-sim-kiaN3. 
  Sun Tai7-pit8 jiat8-sim thoan5 to7-li2 chap8-si3 geh8 jit8 liau2-au7, hut-jian5 jiam2-tioh8 thou3-sia3 e5 piN7. Chit8 e5 peng5-iu2 aN3-loh8 mng7 i kong2, “Li2 e5 sin3-sim sim2-mih8 khoan2, Tai7-pit8 ah?” I soe3-a2-siaN in3 kong2,“Tui3 thau5-khak kau3 kha long2 si7 Gi7.” Hit-si5 i e5 sin5-hun5 tui3 bak8-chiu chio3 chhut chin chheng-pek8. 
  Hut-jian5 lou7-be2-pai2 kap tui3-tek8 tui3-bin7,i bo5 kiaN-hiaN5, in-ui7 i u7 tit-tioh8 Ki-tok oan5-choan5 khoah-toa7 e5 Gi7 e5 Hou7-sim-kiaN3. Sou2-i2 bok8-koai3 i kong2, “Tui3 thau5-khak kau3 kha long2 si7 Gi7.” 
  Chhin-ai3 siau3-lian5 e5 peng, li2 mi5-si5 kui7-loh8, u7-si5 kiam2 bo5 kiaN-hiaN5 a2-si7 kian3-siau3, m7 kaN2 kiN3 Siong7-te3 e5 bin7, in-ui7 tui3 li2 ka-ki7 chai sou2 choe3 u7 m7-tioh8? Sui-bong2 i2-keng jin7 choe7 liau2-au7, iau2-ku2 giau5-gi5 Siong7-te3, soa3 kian3-siau3 m7-kaN2 sui5-pian7 ng3-bang7 sia3-choe7. 
  Hit-si5 li2 tioh8 ui5 Gi7 e5 Hou7-sim-kiaN3, chiu7-si7 Ki-tok it-seng ti7 se3-kan thoe3 lan2 choe3-chiaN5-e5. Siong7-te3 eng7 I siok8 lan2 e5 choe7, sou2-i2 lan2 thang tui3 I choe3-chiaN5 Siong7-te3 e5 Gi7, Chiau3 chit e5 ki5-iN7 e5 iok, li2 thang eng7 li2 e5 choe7 hou7 I taN. Ia7 chiong I oan5-choan5 e5 Gi7 choe3 li2-e5. Au7-lai5 li2 thang chiu7-kun7 Siong7-te3, bo5 chit8-sut-a2 e5 kiaN-hiaN5. 
  Tui3 chit e5 hoat-tou7 hou7 li2 tit-tioh8 gi7, chhin-chhiuN7 sui5-pian7 e5 le2-mih8, an2-ni oe7 hou7 li2 chin khiam-pi; che si7 chin ho2. Chin khiam-pi koh chin hoaN-hi2, ia7 bo5 chit8-sut-a2 e5 kiaN-hiaN5. 
  III. Oe5
  ChiaN geh8 lan2 u7 kang2-kiu3 “Chin-sit8 e5 Toa3.” Teng2 geh8 jit8 u7 gian2-kiu3 “Gi7 e5 Hou7-sim-kiaN3.” Chit geh8 jit8 lan2 tioh8 kang2-kiu3 “Oe5.” 
  Siat-su2 li2 na7 bo5 chiah-e5 khi3-hai5, hek8-si7 beh cheng-chian3 ho2 e5 cheng-chian3, a2-si7 thng3-chhiah-kha beh keng3-chau2, hit si5 li2 e5 tui3-tek8 chiu7 tit-tioh8 ho2 ki-hoe7 thang ti2-tek8 li2. Ti7 lou7-tiong i tek-khak pang3 kou, chhi3-a2, lai7 e5 teng-a2, oe7 tiam e5 chioh8-thau5, chiah-e5 hou7 li2 e5 kha thang3-thiaN3, oe7 ti3-kau3 hou7 li2 sit-taN2. Au7-lai5 tui3-tek8 ki-chhi3 li2 e5 si5 oe7 chhin-chhiuN7 I2-sek-liat8 peh-siN3, in-ui7 to7-lou7 e5 in-toaN sin5-hun5 soa3 sit-taN2 chit8-iuN7. I koh beh hou7 li2 hiam5 choe3-thau5 e5 lang5; hit si5 li2 e5 Ki-tok-tou5 e5 oah8-mia7 chiu7 long2 siu7 sun2-hai7,in-ui7 ai3 hiam5 lang5-e5, long2 boe7 eng5-kng Siong7-te3, ia7 boe7 pang-chan7 lang5 chai I e5 ho2. Lan2 m7-thang thng3-chhiah-kha lai5 keng3-chau2, che kiam2-m7 si7 chin iau3-kin2 mah? Sou2-i2 tioh8 chu3-i3, khoaN3 lan2 e5 kha u7 chheng7 ho5-peng5, hok-im e5 pi7-pan7 a2-bo5. 
  Chong2-si7 chit-tiap8 u7 chit8 hang7 khun3-lan5 e5 su7, chiu7-si7 goa2 boe7 tit beng5-beng5 ka7 lin2 kong2 chit e5 Oe5 si7 sim2-mih8, in-ui7 Seng3-keng bo5 chi2-beng5. Seng3-keng u7 kong2 Chin-sit8 si7 Toa3, Gi7 si7 Hou7-sim-kiaN3, chong2-si7 bo5 chi2-beng5 Oe5 si7 sim2-mih8. Kan-ta kong2 si7 “ho5-peng5 hok-im e5 pi7-pan7.” 
